songs.title: Soaked
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Soaked to the bone
Sink like a stone
Walk home alone
It's not the first time, it's not the worst crime
Your soul will be okay

[Chorus]
When you've had enough
Searching for love
And you miss the touch
Of someone new

[Verse]
Burns by dreams
It's never how it seems
Cold crushed esteem
Take shelter and hide forever
Your soul will be okay

[Chorus]
And you've had enough
Searching for love
But you miss the touch
Of someone new

Ooooohh
Ooooohh

[Chorus]
And I've had enough
Searching for love
But I miss the touch
Of someone new

[Outro]
Soaked to the bone
Sink like a stone
I will take you home
It's not the first time, it's not the worst crime
Our souls will be okay
